&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;em>How does Raiden Thrust work?&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>Raiden Thrust is an upgraded True Thrust. It combos into both Disembowel and Vorpal Thrust and replaces True Thrust on your bar when itâ€™s ready. You activate it by successfully landing the positional on the fifth hit of your combo (Fang and Claw or Wheeling Thrust following Wheeling Thrust or Fang and Claw, respectively). If you fail, you get to press True Thrust and hear a laugh track play in the background.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Dragoon Best in Slot (BiS)</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/best-in-slot/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:24:31 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/best-in-slot/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Stat Priority</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/stat-priority/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:23:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/stat-priority/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Changes</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/job-changes/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:21:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/job-changes/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Advanced Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/advanced-guide/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Sep 2022 20:41:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/advanced-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p>Due to the nature of the Dragoon job design, advanced content is included and covered within the &lt;a href="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/basic-guide/">Basic Guide&lt;/a>. If you have further questions regarding DRG optimization, please feel free to ask in the Discord server.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>